<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Confirmation Failed</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f44336, #b71c1c);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #fff;
            color: #b71c1c;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

            a:hover {
                background: #f1f1f1;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Email Confirmation Failed ❌</h1>
        <p>Sorry <b>{{UserName}}</b>, the confirmation link is invalid or has expired.</p>
        <a href="/resend-confirmation">Resend Confirmation Email</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
